Title: Structure
Definition: Physical structure such as a building or piece of infrastructure.

Title: Product
Definition: Products produced by businesses, which may or may not be physical items.

Title: Disruption (Business Interruption)
Definition: Planned operations or service provision of a business or infrastructure.

Title: Population
Definition: Injuries, fatalities, and displacements of a population.

Title: Indicator or index value
Definition: Value of economic indicator or development index.
